cl-lsm-tree
===========

This software was extracted from CLPIC (Common Lisp P2P Intellectual Property Chain).

Extracted component: src/storage/lsm/

This is a standalone, zero-dependency implementation of a Log-Structured
Merge-tree (LSM-tree) key-value storage engine in pure Common Lisp.

The implementation uses only SBCL built-in facilities:
- sb-thread for threading primitives
- sb-ext for string/octets conversion

No external libraries (Quicklisp packages) are required.
